<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>📝 Your Order Has a Rider!</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 10px; }
    .header { background-color: #2196f3; color: white; padding: 10px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0; }
    .content { padding: 20px; }
    .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #777; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; }
    .highlight { font-weight: bold; color: #2196f3; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      📝 Order Assigned!
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
      <p>Your order <span class="highlight">#{{orderId}}</span> has been assigned to <span class="highlight">{{raiderName}}</span>.</p>
      <p>Raider's rank: <span class="highlight">{{raiderRank}}</span></p>
      <p>Raider's email: <span class="highlight">{{raiderEmail}}</span></p>
      <p>You can now track your order and communicate with your assigned raider.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      Thank you for using our service!
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
